3. Data Collection & Privacy
  Crashbot may collect and process the following types of data:

  User Data: Discord usernames, user IDs, avatars, user activity logs, and other user-related information.
  Server Data: Server names, server IDs, channel names, message logs (if applicable), role information, and administrative settings.
  Bot Interaction Data: Commands used, timestamps, error logs, and other operational data.

